            <p class="card-text">This was a proof of concept for a community based audio recording website that was intended to be used by a library in Redruth UK. It was designed with a minimal use case. Users audio recordings are stored in AWS S3 buckets and data in Mongodb. Western Washington University has taken it on as an ongoing project to expand its use case and explore its potential. If you save a recording it requires the Webmaster to approve it before it becomes available to the public.</p>
